{"tid":1152733,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"呢間舖頭個重慶酸辣牛肉米線真係好與眾不同","createTime":"2019-05-13T07:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T17:06:52.000Z","uid":180545,"like":5,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0959f69162080486794d15263edeeeeb7adc173c","tid":1152733,"uid":180545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T07:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oa6OK6x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foa6OK6x.png&h=db6f3525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 簡直係顛覆咗我對重慶酸辣嘅概念<br />\n我問個店員呢碗係乜嚟<br />\n佢自己望住張單先up得出係重慶酸辣牛肉米線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻show google重慶酸辣俾佢睇 話唔好呃我喎 重慶酸辣係咁㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢講咗句 每間舖做法唔一樣㗎喇 之後黑面走開咗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後問第二個店員 佢話佢哋係用酸菜魚個湯底去整<br />\n咁你重乜撚嘢慶酸辣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vfuMwMB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvfuMwMB.png&h=655d5c9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0219a5a445b7b75674383fece95acd2f66a4b942","tid":1152733,"uid":177440,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"酸辣有好多種 印象中重慶酸辣一定係紅卜卜"},{"pid":"4bf8f0d99a6491def3928cc470f100a0e84ad665","tid":1152733,"uid":180545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0219a5a445b7b75674383fece95acd2f66a4b942","tid":1152733,"uid":177440,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"酸辣有好多種 印象中重慶酸辣一定係紅卜卜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T07:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2098846a8b7334fdfacbe4b838ac16bbc8ac8385","tid":1152733,"uid":247139,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T07:21:35.000Z","msg":"以為你叫酸菜牛肉米線